well last night was a little wierd for me.
all i can say i is I LOVE CHURCH AND GOD.
im glad we all went together.=) like old times...

when we were at church, i got an amazing message from God.
his spirit was so THICK last night. pastor tommy asked us "if your school made an announcement for all saved people to come to the office, how many ppl would actually check out of class?" me and adrianna said there are prolly about 7-9 ppl in our senior class that are saved. and about 40 tops in the whole school. this made me really discouraged. we all have this awesome power of God and only 40 freakin ppl KNOW ABOUT IT?!...that really meant something to me.
then later he asked us to think about "how many ppl in your life right now, know that you love god?" I know that most of the kids in school who know me, know that fact about me. I pretty much surround myself by other spiritual ppl. but then again i thought to myself" if i were to die right now... id want WAY more ppl to know about my faith". it kills me that i know so many athiest'. there are so many that iam friends with. adn taht hurts me everyday, that ppl i love, dont know our lord. =/...
pastor tommy prayed for everyone in the building to be more bold when it comes to spreading the name and power of Christ. i really just want to be strong with it.

then later after service, guilt came upon me. you see, i was pretty much for sure drinking after prom. all my friends are doing it so i figured it'd be the only way to have fun... WRONG! while i was sitting in church i prayed about my choices. God just came over me with my change in decision. NO WAY! how could i even think it? so later at taco bell i called kyle to talk about it, i know he doesnt drink so i needed support. it helped. 

i kept thinking so much on the way home. i felt so guilty. it sucked.

then i talked to good ole' catherine and she said we can maybe go to oasis afterwards. :) thatd be awesome! then even we can maybe stop at jen's and say hi then leave, ya know? it wont be that bad... i always have fun with her! even though we are about to be put through SO much pain in exactly a week! eeps!

i just really want everyone in my life to know who GOd is and what he can do for you. he is an everlasting friend. I really just want to start taking more of my friends to church with me... kat(needs to start coming lol), catherine=), maybe? kyle...someday...thne anyone else who comes.it'd make me SO happy and fufilled!=) thats all i want in life. :)

please know im here to help anyone! even if you think you're doomed and god could never love you for what youve done or said. he always forgives and he will forever love YOU!!!
